            <p><strong>Scope:</strong> Complete theme system examination for Comserv including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>✓ Theme CSS files in `root/static/css/themes/`</li>
                <li>✓ Theme variable definitions in `theme_definitions.json`</li>
                <li>✓ Site-to-theme mappings (which site uses which theme)</li>
                <li>✓ CSS variable availability and usage patterns</li>
                <li>✓ Inline style attributes across all documentation .tt files</li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>Methodology:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>File system scan: `find Comserv/root/static/css/themes/`</li>
                <li>JSON parsing: `theme_definitions.json` structure analysis</li>
                <li>Pattern matching: `grep -r 'style="'` across documentation</li>
                <li>File profiling: Per-file inline style count and ranking</li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>Audit Date:</strong> December 26, 2025 19:25 UTC</p>
